name: Weng Santos
text: Sorry I didn't know that or I wouldn't have tagged you.    Anyway, to my batchmates here, and to Bik  Yonzon , pag na-tokhang kayo call me.  Not as efficient as a robot, but due process goes both ways and I will uphold your right to it.
